  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Limited data exist regarding temporal trends in permanent pacemaker (PPM) implantation. To
      describe trends in incidence and comorbidities of PPM recipients, the investigators aim to
      conduct a retrospective population-based cohort study using record linkage, over a 32 year
      period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
